data.description: Welcome to this exquisite former model home nestled in the charming community of Lake Las Vegas South Shores. Set against the backdrop of awe-inspiring views, this residence offers an unparalleled living experience. The main highlight of this home is undoubtedly its breathtaking views that stretch across the Lake Mead Reserve. The heart of the home boasts an entertainer's dream kitchen with  gorgeous views and  upgraded appliances with a kitchen island. Formal dinning room, private wine room, fireplace.  Living room with custom built in and access to the great out doors. The primary suite, conveniently located on the ground floor, offers a retreat of its own. Dual closets, dual vanities, a spacious shower, and a separate soaking tub create a spa-like ambiance. A private retreat area off the primary suite opens to the courtyard. The primary suite provides access to the backyard, where you can bask in the warmth of summer evenings and unwind in the spa. So Much More! Awe Inspiring!
